on=2018&gist=7ce67b5ecf36009ca4a036743a46224b)\r\n\r\nand simple benchmark for add\r\n\r\n```rust\r\n#![feature(test)]\r\n\r\nextern crate test;\r\n\r\nuse test::{black_box, Bencher};\r\n\r\n#[bench]\r\npub fn foo(b: &mut Bencher) {\r\n    b.iter(|| {\r\n        let mut s: i32 = 0;\r\n        let add = black_box(0);\r\n        for _ in 0..1_000_000 {\r\n            s = black_box(s.saturating_add(add));\r\n        }\r\n    });\r\n}\r\n\r\n#[bench]\r\npub fn bar(b: &mut Bencher) {\r\n    b.iter(|| {\r\n        let mut s: i32 = 0;\r\n        let add = black_box(0);\r\n        for _ in 0..1_000_000 {\r\n            s = black_box(s.checked_add(add).unwrap_or(i32::MAX));\r\n        }\r\n    });\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\n```sh\r\nrustc +nightly-2021-03-17 -Copt-level=3 --test bench.rs\r\n./bench --bench\r\n\r\nrunning 2 tests\r\ntest bar ... bench:     438,332 ns/iter (+/- 8,118)\r\ntest foo ... bench:     875,785 ns/iter (+/- 2,880)\r\n\r\ntest result: ok. 0 passed; 0 failed; 0 ignored; 2 measured; 0 filtered out; finished in 1.59s\r\n```", "closed_by": {"login": "Riey", "id": 14910534, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjE0OTEwNTM0", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/14910534?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/Riey", "html_url": "https://github.com/Riey", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/Riey/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/Riey/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/Riey/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/Riey/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/Riey/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/Riey/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/Riey/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/Riey/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/Riey/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/re